    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The study of manuscripts as physical and cultural artifacts, including all aspects of their structure and manufacture, their interrelationships, and their historical development and impact.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
